fields.title: Bedworth Sofa
fields.body_html:
Bedworth is proof that a neatly tailored, ''put together'' look doesn't mean cramping your relaxed sense of style. Its sofa, loveseat and two choices in accent chairs are dressed to impress and crafted for comfort. Evocative of the classic gray flannel suit, Bedworth sofa, loveseat and matching accent chair are beautifully ''buttoned up'' with decorative nailhead trim, and covered in a softly textured polyester chenille upholstery inspired by fashionable menswear. Their reversible coil seating enhances both structure and support, as does durable frame construction. Exposed legs don an espresso faux wood finish. For a splash of color, there's Bedworth other accent chair: a classic wingback with sloped arms that's upholstered in a springy, vibrant fabric carried through in the sofa and loveseat's pair of accent pillows.

fields.title: Emerfield Bedroom Set
fields.body_html:
Transform your bedroom into a haven with a chic look that combines the best of a sleek urban style with the warmth of wood with the Emerfield Bedroom Set from the Emerfield Collection by Ashley Furniture. This stylish set features a striking two-tone finish that combines a black rubbed finish with a dark rustic wood tone and light distressing for a smart, worn look. Oil-rubbed bronze hardware nods toward the vintage inspiration for this set. This set includes a queen bed, six-drawer dresser, mirror, and three-drawer nightstand. The bed features classic sleigh styling with a wide-plank headboard and footboard. The drawers feature solid rubberwood fronts, dovetail construction, and ball bearing drawer glides for smooth and durable operation.  The top drawers on the dresser, chest, and nightstand are all lined with black felt.

fields.title: Enso Affinity Hybrid Mattress
fields.body_html:
The Affinity mattress utilizes the best of advanced Gel Infused Memory Foam, PureGel®; with the unique conforming characteristics found with individually wrapped coil innersprings. We start with a ThermaCool knit fabric which allows cool air to flow throughout the mattress. We then apply the Gel Spheres directly to the layer of PureGel® Infused memory foam providing a cool, conforming, comfort layer. A layer of high density comfort foam allows for a supportive, yet comfortable experience. The Comfort Support Core features 7 inch individually wrapped coils on a layer of ultra high density base foam. These coils are encased in Enso border edge foam allowing for a firm seat edge and extra support when sleeping out to the edge. 

DIMENSIONS

Twin: 38" W x 75" D x 13" H

Full: 54" W x 75" D x 13" H

fields.title: Enso Calle Hybrid Mattress
fields.body_html:
The Calle mattress features a Tencel™ zip on cover that is 100% machine washable. The Total Surface Coverage Gel Memory Foam positions the gel layer as close to the sleeper's body as possible, enhancing the ability to conform to the unique shape of the individual, while all but eliminating painful pressure points.  A 2" layer of luxury firm Memory Foam adds supportive comfort to the Calle.  The Comfort Support Core features an innerspring made with 7" individually wrapped coils on an ultra-high density support base.  The Comfort Core is encased with an HD foam border providing a firm seat edge and extra support when sleeping out to the edge of the mattress.

fields.title: Guardsman 5 Year Elite Plan
fields.body_html:
Guardsman is a leader in the furniture protection and care industry for almost 100 years. Consumers trust Guardsman to help protect their furniture and keep it looking new and without blemish. Whether it's fabric, wood, or leather, the goal of our protection plans is to help people get their furniture repaired quickly. Nothing gives you more confidence and satisfaction than knowing that your furniture purchases will remain beautiful and valuable for as long as possible. With Guardsman® Furniture Protection Plan, you will have peace of mind knowing that your new fabric, leather, wood, and many other types of furniture are protected from accidental stains and damage. These plans provide you with a furniture repair expert when you need one across the United States and Canada.

The Protection includes:

- Spot Cleaning of Accidental Food & Beverage Stains, household stains, ballpoint pen stains, lipstick, nail polish, nail polish remover, cometics, human and pet body fluids (except perspiration, hair & body oils)
- Repair of accidental damaged zippers, button breakage, seam seperations, punctures, rips, cuts, tears and burns to most leathers and fabrics.
- Repair of accidental burns, heat marks, scratches and gouges to wood
- Repair of accidental damage to springs, frames, and certain mechanisms

If Guardsman cannot clean or repair, they will reupholster the damaged area. If the material is no longer available, then Guardsman  will offer replacement options.  Animal physical damage is not covered.

To find out more, please call us at 631-768-8130.

Sealy Posturepedic® Mattresses are known for their comfort and all-over support so your body can fully relax and you can get the sleep you need. This collection features the support of the Sealy Embrace™ Coil: Specially engineered encased coil system that responds to the natural curves and alignment of your spine, for full-body support. fields.title: Sealy Massachusetts Avenue Plush Euro Pillow Top Mattress
fields.body_html:
The Sealy Posturepedic Massachusetts Ave Plush Euro Pillowtop mattress is easily one of the softest mattresses in the collection. Back and side sleepers who love nice cloud-like comfort and support will love this mattress. We recommend that stomach sleepers check out the cushion firm pillow top option instead of this one, as it will be much more comfortable for your back.

The Plush euro pillow top mattress does put most of its emphasis on comfort with its incredibly soft upper layers, but since it is a Posturepedic mattress, it does not skimp on support. With the Sealy Embrace Coil at the heart of its support system, this mattress provides all the same support of the rest of the collection, with individually wrapped coils that are more capable of contouring to your unique shape to provide personalized support and comfort. Personalized support will ensure that you sleep more deeply, and for longer.

fields.title: Sierra Power Base
fields.body_html:
Take sleep to a whole new level. With the "zero gravity" pre-set position, weightlessness is simulated and pressure points are eliminated. Raise your legs to increase blood circulation and relieve pressure on your lower back. Raise your upper body too. The benefits include: comfort for those who want to sit up in bed and better breathing, essential for those who snore or experience acid reflux. Two convenient USB ports are located at the head of the frame for connecting your laptop. Wall hugging adjustable base stays away from headboards and footboards for smooth, silent motion. Platform or storage bed frame is compatible.

Maximize comfort with the addon massage feature that lets you choose and save a preferred intensity setting from a wireless remote. Plus, with the touch of a button, turn on LED lighting for soft illumination under the bed.

fields.title: Tess 3-Piece Sleeper Sectional
fields.body_html:
This sectional sofa with sleeper mattress features a clean and tidy style that will have your home looking updated and uncluttered. It features straight lines throughout its frame and is edged by thick track arms, a token element of modern and contemporary furniture designs. The seat cushions are removable allowing for easier cleaning while the back cushions remain in place. Wooden feet and the three included accent pillows supply simple details to the piece that are decorative but don't make this sectional come across as being over-adorned. When company comes to visit, just pull out the hidden innerspring queen sleeper mattress to accommodate them for the evening. Push this sectional sofa into a corner or use it for room separation, either way you'll have a great new look for your living room or family room display.

fields.title: Zyler Loveseat
fields.body_html:
What do you get when you blend the most soothing of earth tones with pillow soft decadence and chic tailoring? The Zyler loveseat. With smooth-gliding reclining and a gentle rocking element, its poetry in motion. Merging a clean-lined profile with ultra plushness, it manages to be sleek and sumptuous at the same time.
